&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Setting up work items for review&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Rational Team Concert allows you to set work items for approval, review, or verification.&amp;nbsp; In this tool mentor we&#xD;
    will focus on reviews, however the approval and verification feature are very similar. A work item may be a feature,&#xD;
    task, enhancement, track build item, risk, use case,&amp;nbsp;or scenario.&amp;nbsp; Setting up a review for any of these work&#xD;
    item types is the same.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ol>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Open the work item you want to have reviewed.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Select the Approvals tab.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Click the New Approval button.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Select the type of Approval, for this example&amp;nbsp;select Review.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Change the Subject to correspond with the type of approval, for this example we will use Review &amp;lt;task&#xD;
        name&amp;gt;yymmdd.&amp;nbsp; This way you can create multiple reviews for the same task and keep track of each review.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Optionally include a due date.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Select Add Approver...&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        If the reviewers are not listed in the Matching Users field,&amp;nbsp;enter part of the name of the person you would&#xD;
        like to add and click Search.&amp;nbsp; You may select multiple users by using ctrl and clicking their name.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Once you have all the reviewers selected click Ok.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ol>Now you have successfully set up your work item to be reviewed.&amp;nbsp; Notify the reviewer(s) of the work items to&#xD;
review.&amp;nbsp; If the reviewer(s) can view the work item by typing in&amp;nbsp;the the work item number on the bottom left, or&#xD;
do a search for all of the work items which need reviewing&amp;nbsp;by selecting &quot;Pending approvals for me&quot; under the shared&#xD;
queries folder.&amp;nbsp;</mainDescription>
